Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Hokuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:36.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:45.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I-It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:52.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It seems you are awake, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Jeeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I brought coffee for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It sounded like you were having a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You were talking deliriously\N and saying something like "meat, meat."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shall we have grilled meat for today's dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're having various problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:16.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad1.5}Various problems {\fscx169.937}←{\fscx113.291} Please read the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think you should rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I know everything about you, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You've worked for my family\Nfor a long time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:29.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, I see you every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but there's something that\NI just noticed for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've seen your face somewhere, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.38,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Cromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hokuto, you wanted to ask me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have one thing that I wanna ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do you have a grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? A grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:57.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do. But he's a very odd person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:00.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For a long time, he kept starting\Nvarious businesses and failed each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that, in the end, he started saying\Nthat he wanted to own a coffee farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and left his family for Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We don't know where he's been since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder where he is and what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do you still feel like you\Nwanna see him, even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if it were possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}The Hokuto House
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You asked for me, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's someone I want you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Someone you want me to meet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask an abrupt question,\Nbut don't you have a grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They were unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.13,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArnold 2.1\pos(358,210)\fs56\shad0\c&H335C69&\bord1.5\blur0.4\3c&H263536&}Start Me Up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:04:00.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Mechazawa's\Nbeen bummed out these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:04.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, every person's got\Ndifferent worries, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You say every person, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:12.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mecha-ratta, mecha-ratta,\Nmecha-ratta, mecha-ratta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's Mechazawa's little brother, Beta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's carrying something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is...
